d, Gemifloxacin, Lomefloxacin, Cinoxacin, Delafloxacin, Sparfloxacin, Ofloxacin, Pantoprazole, More', 'Imatinib, Dabrafenib, Acalabrutinib, Dacomitinib, Tepotinib, Fedratinib, Avapritinib, Larotrectinib, Selumetinib, Cobimetinib, Capmatinib, More', 'Moderate', NULL, 'DDInter', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/130308/', '[1] "Product Information. Zydelig (idelalisib)." Gilead Sciences, Foster City, CA.[2] "Product Information. Hivid (zalcitabine)." Roche Laboratories, Nutley, NJ.', 1767369485);
